<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            color: #000;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .card {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            /* width: 640px; */
            height: 80%;
            /* margin: auto; */
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }        .image {
            padding-top: 50px;
            display: block;
        }
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .wrapper {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            color: #000;
        }
        .decoration {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .magic-link {
            color: white;
            background-color: blue;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .magic-link {
            width: auto;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .color-black {
            color: #000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #ddd; width: 100%">
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('./header.ejs') %>
            <hr style="margin:0" />
            <div class="card">
                <h4 class="color-black"><b>Greetings from Scaffold</b></h4>
                <h4 class="color-black">Dear <%= firstName %> , </h4>
                <p class="color-black">I wanted to let you know that your role has been updated on our Scaffold workspace. Your new role is <%= role %>, which means that you now have <%= spaceName %> permissions.</p>
                <div class="wrapper">
                    <p class="color-black">We made this change because we believe that your new role is a better fit for your skills and expertise, and will help us collaborate more effectively.</p>
                       
                    <p class="color-black">If you have any questions or concerns about your new role, please don't hesitate to reach out to me or anyone else on the team. </p>
                    <p class="color-black">Thank You,</p>
                    <p class="color-black"><b>Scaffold Team</b></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="margin:0" />
            <%- include('./footer.ejs') %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>